# Event filter groups template for pika-port-kafka.
# Usage: ./pika_port ... -F /path/to/filters.conf
# One group per line. Empty lines and lines starting with # are ignored.
# Syntax: key=PATTERN;type=TYPE1,TYPE2;action=CMD1,CMD2
# Omit any field to match any value in that dimension.
# key patterns:
#   - prefix match if it ends with * and has no other regex meta (dev:topic:*)
#   - regex match if it contains regex meta chars (.*[]()|^$+?\\)
#   - exact match otherwise
# Example group:
# key=dev:topic:*;type=list;action=rpush
